        <title>ACTIVITY: To use appropriate measuring instruments [LO 4.6.2]</title>
        <para id="id11926003">1. Let's talk about measuring jugs!</para>
        <para id="id8802344">1.1 For what reason might your mother or father use a measuring jug at home?</para>
