    <section id="id12490332">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id7720210"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Learning Outcome 4:</emphasis></emphasis>The learner will be able to use appropriate measuring units, instruments and formulae in a variety of contexts.</para>
      <para id="id8945953"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Assessment Standard 4.6:</emphasis></emphasis> We know this when the learner uses appropriate measuring instruments (with understanding of their limitations) to appropriate levels of precision including:</para>
      <para id="id10495859">4.6.2: measuring jugs to measure capacity.</para>
    </section>
